            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine Domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, (…) anni domini
                        MCLXXXVIII, VII idus ian., indictione VI (…). Manifestus sum ego
                                <persName><name ref="Deotisalvi">Deotisalvi</name></persName> filius
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Hubertellus">Ubertelli</name></persName> quia
                        per hanc cartulam venditionis vendo et trado tibi <persName><name
                                ref="Gratianus">Gratiano</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Gratia">Gratie</name></persName> videlicet unum petium terre
                        positum al Melo et terrefinatus ab una parte cum terra <persName><name
                                ref="Ceredanus">Cerretani</name></persName>, secunda parte cum terra
                                <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Gregorius">Gregorii</name></persName>, a tertia
                                <persName><name ref="Silcius/Grillus">Silci
                            Grillii</name></persName>, a quarta parte Gratiani. (…)
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: libras sex. <foreign>Testimoni</foreign>:
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wilgia">Guilia</name></persName>
                        (…).</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
